{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 216745, "create_time": 1655208348, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "赢麻了", "timestamp": 1655208348}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 216884, "create_time": 1655210948, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "中国是典型的警察国家", "timestamp": 1655210948}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 216886, "create_time": 1655210999, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "新加坡怕自己丢皇位怕到骨子里了，思之令人发笑", "timestamp": 1655210999}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 216968, "create_time": 1655212759, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "地主也会没有余粮的", "timestamp": 1655212759}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 217048, "create_time": 1655214118, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "感觉很神奇。主要是针对一些细节比较奇怪，如果真是警察的话，根本不需要暴力破门而入，看过警察执法视频的都知道，如果是临时突击查住在酒店的人，警察会直接练习并控制前台，要求其配合给出房卡，然后直接上去敲门询问开门，不开就直接用房卡刷开而不是暴力破门。因为暴力破门执行任务的人还得自己掏钱给人家把门赔了，而直接用房卡既安全、又方便还不花钱，还容易掩饰（比如伪装成酒店工作人员临时维修一类的）。而且暴力执法很容易收到投诉，特别是现在这种督查、纪委直接向上负责、舆论发达的情况下。简而言之，这种工作作风不像普通警察", "timestamp": 1655214118}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 217186, "create_time": 1655215966, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 如果你有听说地方政府如何截留进京上访的人，就不会对此感到奇怪了", "timestamp": 1655215966}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 217587, "create_time": 1655220242, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 不，地方政府截留上访的也是一样，他们会在车上、路上、进你家的时候使用暴力，但是绝对不会在进酒店房间的时候使用，因为根本不需要，警察又不是拳击狂魔，他使用暴力是为了达成目的，能不使用暴力达成目的SB才使用，因为使用暴力会给自己带来麻烦。任务是上级的，麻烦是自己的。", "timestamp": 1655220242}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 218079, "create_time": 1655234663, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "我估计是对于网络聊天筛查出了错。我们所有的app聊天都是透明的，可能监控中以为是上访或者维权的人。 说截访的人，不使用暴力的。看着不顺眼，自己蹲累了，领导训话了。逮住当事人都是一顿打。", "timestamp": 1655234663}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 219081, "create_time": 1655272042, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Eve: 打当事人没事，因为在拘捕的时候，人受伤是直接去合作医院报销；可是你把人家第三方的门搞坏了只能你自己赔了", "timestamp": 1655272042}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 219302, "create_time": 1655275000, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "凡事不能只听一面之词\n", "timestamp": 1655275000}], "create_time": 1655208143, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1655275000, "likenum": 13, "n_attentions": 13, "n_comments": 10, "pid": 65285, "poll": null, "reply": 10, "text": "[![X5hiaF.jpg](https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/06/14/X5hiaF.jpg)](https://imgtu.com/i/X5hiaF)\n[![X5hV2R.jpg](https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/06/14/X5hV2R.jpg)](https://imgtu.com/i/X5hV2R)\n[![X5h3PH.jpg](https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/06/14/X5h3PH.jpg)](https://imgtu.com/i/X5h3PH)\n[![X5htMt.jpg](https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/06/14/X5htMt.jpg)](https://imgtu.com/i/X5htMt)\n", "timestamp": 1655208143}}